result.name: A Happy Pancake Causeway Bay

reviews.text:
Only food can comfort me in this chaotic time. Dessert always performs its duty diligently with its comforting sweetness. My friend and I visited A Happy Pancake for a pre-show dinner. We never expected this magical souffle pancakes can make us so happy.

My friend ordered a chocolate one, and I got this milk tea one. The milk tea dressing tasted like earl grey, very delicious! My friend’s chocolate sauce was great too, much like nutella and very filling.

The pancake itself was fantastic! It’s so airy and fluffy! Almost felt like melting in our mouths!

Best part was the cream, it was so smooth and went so well with the pancake and dressing!

Granola on top made a surprisingly great match with the pancake. Very yum!

It surely is A Happy Pancake! Probably the best in town.

Visited this pancake house since it’s really famous. Not surprisingly long queue, but the time is worth the wait. Pancakes served in 15 minutes after ordering them, hot and fresh, with thick chocolate syrup. Drinks are good too!
No pancake with beverage set. Beverage order separately. There are choices of sweet or salty pancake dish.

Not my favourite pancake place. Tried the strawberry cheese fondue Soufflé Pancake. You must eat the pancake with the toppings, if not the pancake is very bland and tasteless. The pancakes alone is not sweet at all. The cheese fondue topping is a little different and does not suit my taste. 

Also tried the royal milk tea, this tea was pretty good, different from the classic Hong Kong milk tea. 

There’s a minimum order per person and you cannot add additional items to your order after your order is made.

A popular dessert Cafe originally from Japan specializing in souffle pancakes. Always crowded with long queue. Average waiting time is thirty minutes. The souffle pancakes are divided into dessert and savory categories. Very nice presentation, so popular among foodies.

result.name: 幸福班戟 銅鑼灣店

reviews.text:
🥞芝士慕絲雜莓醬班戟（$128）
班戟充滿蛋香味，質感上有空氣感但比Flipper's嘅實少少，配埋隔離嘅cream cheese加牛奶忌廉都十分輕盈，好好食！另外雜莓醬微酸，味道似藍莓果醬，配cream同班戟似New York cheese cake味。
-
🥞全麥班㦸配芝士蘑菇奄列（$118）
全麥班戟本來以為會好乾好硬，點知係完全相反！鬆軟程度不亞於甜食班戟，仲多咗啲小麥嘅口感🤤奄列味道不過不失，中間芝士可以拉絲不過食落去存在感不大😂
- 
題外話：而家有得上網訂位，唔洗排隊！

Only food can comfort me in this chaotic time. Dessert always performs its duty diligently with its comforting sweetness. My friend and I visited A Happy Pancake for a pre-show dinner. We never expected this magical souffle pancakes can make us so happy.

My friend ordered a chocolate one, and I got this milk tea one. The milk tea dressing tasted like earl grey, very delicious! My friend’s chocolate sauce was great too, much like nutella and very filling.

The pancake itself was fantastic! It’s so airy and fluffy! Almost felt like melting in our mouths!

Best part was the cream, it was so smooth and went so well with the pancake and dressing!

Granola on top made a surprisingly great match with the pancake. Very yum!

It surely is A Happy Pancake! Probably the best in town.

剛好有天放假心血來潮
一早到了幸福班戟
為了不用排隊做第一批坐上客
點了期間限定的Tiramisu pancake 🥞
當然還有一冰解膩的美式咖啡☕️
濃濃的暖朱古力醬拌著香軟輕柔的梳乎厘pancake
還有淡淡然的mascarpone mousse and cream
一口一口都是幸福的滋味
一邊聽著店家精選的日系歌曲
不知不覺就享受完畢整碟pancake😌

果然，有幸福的感覺❤️❤️❤️
鬆軟cake係好味，但最後一口有紙包蛋糕的味道。7點半店外沒有人龍，但工作壓力大的員工不斷來回左右，我relax唔到，唉。食完舒服少少，因為今晚8點半後只坐了一半座位。

4點半左右等10分鐘就能入座 比預期的快多了！
跟日本的不太一樣 原味鬆餅只配楓糖漿奶油 鮮奶油要另點呢 （我當然有點啦）
·
沒期望太高是對的因為跟日本的還是不能比 沒什麼蛋香也不夠空氣感 口感偏乾
楓糖漿也很奇怪的苦澀
只可以勉強解解饞 哈哈
